{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778603464662,"sessionID":"ses_1e2f95729ffeb7En2m5FzdeG8S","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-ad81768d2ac82d71","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json"},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"**Uberon term**\\r\\nhttp://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0009834\\r\\n\\r\\n**Bug description**\\r\\nThis is not necessarily a bug - just a question at this point - but there wasn't another category of new issue to choose. I notice that 'dorsolateral prefrontal cortex' http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0009834 is a sibling of 'prefrontal cortex' http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0000451 but it seems to me that it should be a part_of child of it instead.\\r\\n\\r\\nBest,\\r\\nMichelle\\r\\n\\r\\nThis term question arose as part of work on the SCORCH Project (Single Cell Opioid Response in the Context of HIV).\\r\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86oZFHi\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"mgiglio99\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"NONE\",\n10:       \"body\": \"Looping in @JPReceveur who works on this project too.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-04-23T18:22:08Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3447#issuecomment-2825146850\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86snI64\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"dosumis\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"This is consistent with the Allen Brain Atlas, which I think should be our source of truth for this.  \\n\\n<img width=\\\"357\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/df31bfc3-dd6b-4606-90be-7d22d493da67\\\" />\\n\\n http://atlas.brain-map.org/atlas?atlas=138322603#structure=10172\\n\\n@dragon-ai-agent  - please change the part relationship from 'dorsolateral prefrontal cortex' to 'cerebral cortex' to a part relationship to 'prefrontal cortex'.\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-05-20T22:06:20Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n31:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3447#issuecomment-2895941304\",\n32:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n33:     },\n34:     {\n35:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86vuaTs\",\n36:       \"author\": {\n37:         \"login\": \"mgiglio99\"\n38:       },\n39:       \"authorAssociation\": \"NONE\",\n40:       \"body\": \"Thanks very much @dosumis \\nBest,\\nMichelle\\n\",\n41:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-06-06T05:51:31Z\",\n42:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n43:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n44:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n45:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n46:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3447#issuecomment-2948179180\",\n47:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n48:     },\n49:     {\n50:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86xbEvE\",\n51:       \"author\": {\n52:         \"login\": \"dosumis\"\n53:       },\n54:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n55:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please change the part relationship on 'dorsolateral prefrontal cortex' from 'cererbral cortex' to 'prefrontal cortex'\",\n56:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-06-16T13:28:25Z\",\n57:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n58:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n59:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n60:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n61:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3447#issuecomment-2976664516\",\n62:       \"view