{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778604225524,"sessionID":"ses_1e2f95729ffeb7En2m5FzdeG8S","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-8e48526e61890738","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary of Changes\n- Updated the `part_of` relationship for the term `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` (UBERON:0009834).\n- Changed the parent from `cerebral cortex` (UBERON:0000956) to `prefrontal cortex` (UBERON:0000451).\n\n## Rationale\n- This change was requested based on the Allen Brain Atlas, as noted in the issue discussion. \n- The `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` is an anatomical part of the `prefrontal cortex`, which in turn is a part of the `cerebral cortex`. By updating this relationship to the more specific parent, the ontology's hierarchical accuracy is improved.\n\n## Validation\n- Verified the existence and IDs of both `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` (UBERON:0009834) and `prefrontal cortex` (UBERON:0000451).\n- Used `obo-checkout` and `obo-checkin` for the edit.\n- Reserialized the ontology using `robot convert`.\n- Verified the change with `git diff`.\n","filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778604225517,"end":1778604225523}},"id":"prt_e1d11d461001R6pQv8euVqtEuW","sessionID":"ses_1e2f95729ffeb7En2m5FzdeG8S","messageID":"msg_e1d11ce44001Xxv4k35AElXb7J"}}
